&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.hedonismresorts.com/?gclid=CLWMifS7vqsCFZAAQAodAh7_vw', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/HedonismResorts?ref=share', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;This resort requires $150 USD per week to be paid into the gift fund and will automatically be charged with your order.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 426, 489],
                [172, '', '&lt;p&gt;Proceed to The Jewell Resorts&amp;nbsp; transportation desk located outside customs area in the arrival hall for your free shuttle to the resort.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', 'Runaway Bay', 0, '', 517, 'Reid', 'Swain', '876-973-2436', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Airport transfers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;are not included&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for this resort for&amp;nbsp;booked dates&amp;nbsp;after January 1 2019. You are able to book your transfers to and from MBJ, &amp;nbsp;Donald Sangster International airport, via the following link:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;If you are looking for a shared option and do not see it, please email us to set it up for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Fitness/Zumba Professionals and Yoga: 8am one hour, 9am half hour and 3pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;11:00-11:30am Aqua if applicable&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Golf Pros: 9:00AM &amp;ndash; 12PM&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tennis: 8AM to 10PM; 4PM to 5PM,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;*Do not rely on the kids club&amp;nbsp;during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I\'ve worked with this resort since it was Breezes Runaway Bay and it\'s always a favorite. The updates to the resort are fantastic and lovely to take advantage of the golfing.&lt;/p&gt;', 'https://www.jewelresorts.com/resorts/runawaybay', 'Denise', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/jewelresorts', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires $150 USD per week, plus $75 USD for each child 13 and younger.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;In some instances Fit Bodies, Inc. may collect the gift fund for the purchase of larger items requested by the resort.&amp;nbsp; Golf pros will bring golf clubs for juniors as their gift.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to Jamaica is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 431, 489],
