                [174, '', '', '', '242-327-3298', '', '', 0, '', 517, 'McPhee', 'Carlton', '242-327-5356', 'Alison@fitbodiesinc.com', '242-327-3298', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are included. Ask for Breezes shuttle upon arrival into the Nassau airport.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule M-F&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;(Tentative and subject to change)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 9:00am or 4:30pm cardio or Zumba 1:30pm aqua&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suzelle&amp;rsquo;s comments:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;One of the first places Fit Bodies Inc. sent pros.&amp;nbsp; I taught there right after New Years Y2K.&amp;nbsp; I love the park across the street which is a great place to get a nice run in without getting sand in your shoes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
