                [176, 'A great resort in Jamaica...', 'Proceed to the Superclubs transportation desk located outside customs area in the arrival hall for your free shuttle to the resort.', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 'James', 'Sam', '876954-0000', 'sam.james@superclubs.com', '', '', 'Proceed to the Superclubs transportation desk located outside customs area in the arrival hall for your free shuttle to the resort.', '', null, 'The schedule is TBA and based on your fitness specialties.  Generally, there are 2-3 classes per day.', '<em>What a great set-up.  BracoVillage is exactly that – a resort with a village in the middle.  What is so great about this resort is that in the evening, every restaurant empties in the square where the disco, piano bar and outside tables and chairs encourage everyone to mingle.  The beach on the au natural side is so large that you can hang with friends or have alone time as well.  I got certified to dive here over in 1998.</em>
