&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;NO BAD DAYS!!&amp;nbsp; The sun shines every day in Los Cabos. They had no rain in 2011 and normally it is 5 days for about 20 minutes.&amp;nbsp; The beach goes forever and the waves are incredible.&amp;nbsp; Come here in the fall to experience a guaranteed sunny vacation or winter to watch the whales.&amp;nbsp; Anytime is the right time to be in Los Cabos!!&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://desireloscabos.com', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/DesireResorts', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This resort requires $200 per week to be paid into the gift fund and will automatically be charged with your order.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 442, 499],
                [179, '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office. Once you book this resort, a Fit Bodies representative will be in touch with transfer details. For transfer questions,&amp;nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Erica@fitbodiesinc.com?subject=Transfers&quot;&gt;email Erica&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '809-412-2288', '', 'Punta Cana', 0, '', 596, 'Pfeil', 'Sandy', '809-476-7777', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '8094122288', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel, after your secure your flight.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Punta-Cana-%28PUJ%29-Airport-Transfers/&quot;&gt;Punta Cana Bavaro Transfers &lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt; will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;9:00-10:00am yoga, pilates or stretching&lt;br /&gt; 12-1:00 water gym (sometimes taught or shared with resort staff*)&lt;br /&gt; 4:30pm group fitness or yoga/pilates (sometimes taught by resort staff*)&lt;br /&gt; Personal Trainers work in the gym 1 to 2 hours in the morning&lt;br /&gt; *Resort staff teach several of the classes. Plan to participate when appropriate.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Schedule for tennis pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 10-11am each day all other appointments as per requested by the guest&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Resort hosts 3 teaching vacation positions each week either Group Fitness, Yoga/Pilates, Personal Trainer or Tennis Pro.&lt;/p&gt;
