                [180, '&lt;p&gt;Two sessions only at this time Nov 29 2015&amp;nbsp;through December 17 2015 and Dec 15&amp;nbsp;through January&amp;nbsp;5 2016.&amp;nbsp;These dates allow two days on each side of the classes for arrival and orientation.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', '', 80, '', 453, 'Connor', 'Cardigan', '', '', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Flight lands in St. Maarten&lt;/p&gt;
