                [182, '&lt;p&gt;
	Starfish Trelawny is located in beautiful mature gardens on a long stretch of white sand beach, nestled against lush green mountains and turquoise Caribbean Sea. This well established inclusive resort is ideal for families seeking comfortable, well-equipped accommodations with a wide range of amenities. Adults and children alike can take advantage of the many activities during the day and nightly evening entertainment. Sports enthusiasts enjoy a wide variety of both land and water sports.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;
