                [195, '', '&lt;p&gt;Once you arrive at the airport and have passed customs, proceed to the Couples arrival lounge. A van or bus will take you to the resort.&lt;/p&gt;', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/65816_coupleslogo.jpg', '', '', 'Ocho Rios', 0, '', 517, 'Bailey', 'Charmaine', '8769754439', 'corom@couples.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Contact - ????? TBA before reopening Res Manager - Gretchen Cadian corresmgr@couples.com Phone Number - &lt;a href=&quot;tel:876 975 4271&quot;&gt;876 975 4271&lt;/a&gt; Larry shipping equipment soon - ck to find out if we have trades&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Once you arrive at the airport and have passed customs, proceed to the Couples arrival lounge. A van or bus will take you to the resort.&amp;nbsp; Transfers are only included from Montego Bay airport.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yoga or Pilates Instructors:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; Classes are 1 hour&lt;br /&gt; Mon thru Fri - &amp;nbsp;7:30 or 8am (depending on season) &amp;amp; 4pm&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Group Fitness, or Zumba w/Aqua:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; Classes are 1 hour&lt;br /&gt; Mon &amp;ndash; Thurs 9am &amp;amp; 5pm; Fri 9am and 4pm&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
