                [200, '&lt;p&gt;
	This hotel is great for Singles, Couples or Families. Crown Paradise Club Resort offers an inclusive package without limits that you may not know where to start and that you will never want to end. Crown Paradise Club has everything. Water park for the kids with a Pirate ship and 8 water slides, excellent a la carte dining at 5 restaurants and buffet dining, adult only areas (swimming pool, separate area in buffet dining room and adults only bar and restaurant), mini golf, disco, nightly entertainment, Also included is 24 hour room service, 2 snack bars open around the clock. Children&amp;rsquo;s programs start at 18 months. Close to important destination features such as nightclubs, shopping plazas, restaurants and a short drive to archaeological sites, and botanical gardens. Mexican culture loves families and kids and Crown Paradise Club promise to you to make this a Mexican fun filled vacation with endless activities for all ages. Two children 12 and under included in the administration fee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
