&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgba[255, 255, 255, 0);&quot;&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to the islands&amp;nbsp;is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 427, 489],
                [208, '', '&lt;p&gt;Book your transfer using our preferred provider, Lomas. www.lomas-travel.com/fitbodies&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', 'Carretera Federal 387, KM 299', 'Solidaridad, Playa del Carmen , Qui', 80, '', 592, 'Tinedo', 'Luis', '(52) 984.873.4880', 'missy@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Schedule is 9am pilates and 10am yoga. REgardless of teaching abilities, the times will be the same.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Not included but you can book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel. Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Jamaica-South-Transfers/&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 2 Transfers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions. Erica will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher via before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Mon-Sat&lt;br /&gt;8:30 yoga or stretch&lt;br /&gt;9:30 second yoga class, sculpt or pilates formatting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I stayed here several years ago while on a business trip to drum up some new resorts.&amp;nbsp; That one was not on the list but after staying there we decided to speak to the manager.&amp;nbsp; Three years later we are working with the entire chain.&amp;nbsp; This property is gorgeous.&amp;nbsp; Get a chair by the pool early &amp;ndash; I noticed that a book was on every chair when I went out for my early morning run.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.secretsresorts.com/capri/index.html', 'Missy Pope', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/SecretsCapri', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
