                [211, '', '', '', '', 'Road To Veracruz Km 7', 'Panama City', 80, '', 458, 'Manager', 'Entertainment Team', '', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Resort is located about 35 minutes from the Tocumen International Airport. Transfers are not included. &amp;nbsp;Expect to grab a taxi when you arrive at the airport. &amp;nbsp;Uber is also available. &amp;nbsp;We also suggest a taxi from the hotel to the airport as well.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Yoga and Pilates only - teach 8am and 9am yoga and or pilates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Fitness instructors teach 8am Stretch Yoga or Pilates and 9am&amp;nbsp;Cardio, strength or sculpt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Zumba onlly instructors teach 11am and&amp;nbsp;3pm Zumba&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Aqua only teach &amp;nbsp;8am stretch and 12pm Aqua&lt;br /&gt;Personal Training schedule is small group sessions of sculpt, stretch, bootcamp and so forth at two times during the day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
