                [212, '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included. Fit Bodies, Inc. will contact you to schedule airport transfers prior to your scheduled trip. In Jamaica we use Jamaica Tours Ltd. (JTL) The desk is located at the back left corner of the Montego Bay Airport. You must schedule your transfers through our office first and then your reservation will be made and your name will be included on their list.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', 'Lucea', 0, '', 517, '', 'Bow Wow', '876-619-0000', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;3rd child is $62 per night. Over 12 or third adult is $92. They allow 4 in a room.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included with this teaching vacation. You may book your transfer with our partners at JTL-Jamaica Tours Limited online via their website. Click &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to schedule in advance.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fitness Professionals&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stretching at 10:00am;&amp;nbsp;Cardio/Zumba at 10:30;&amp;nbsp;Aquaerobics at 12:00pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tennis Professionals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Monday thru Friday &lt;br /&gt;Mon &amp;ndash; Friday 8:00 &amp;ndash; 8:45 Advanced Tennis Clinic; 9:00 &amp;ndash; 9:45 Beginners Tennis Clinic; &lt;br /&gt;Tues and Thurs 4:00 &amp;ndash; 4:45 Childrens Tennis Clinic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Fiesta America has created quite an oasis in Lucea.&amp;nbsp; This property is very large and perfect for families.&amp;nbsp; BUT singles and couples should try it because of the disco, the adult pools, adult restaurants and late morning classes so you don&amp;rsquo;t have to wake up early after a party night.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.fiestahotelgroup.com/index.php/en/hoteles/destinos/caribe/jamaica_montego_bay/jamaica_montego_bay/grand_palladium_lady_hamilton_resort_spa', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented to your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to the islands&amp;nbsp;is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 428, 489],
                [213, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/17906_DREPA.jpg', '', '', 'Puerto Aventuras', 0, '', 592, 'Briceno', 'Victor', '(52) 984.875.3000', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Schedule-yoga at 9am everyday. Mon. cardio 12noon,pilates 4pm. Tues. aqua 12-12:30,cardio 4pm Wed. cardio12 Thurs. aqua 12, cardio 4 Fri cardio 12 Sat. aqua 12, pilates 4pm&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&amp;nbsp;Book your round trip transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel. &amp;nbsp;After securing flights, go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Cancun-%28CUN%29-Airport-Transfers-Zone-3/&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 3 Transfers&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica will be in touch via email with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Teach Mon-Sat. Resort hosts one pro per week either yoga, pilates, group fitness, personal trainer or zumba. If you are personal trainer then you\'ll offer small group training sessions incorporating stretch, sculpt, bootcamp skills and so forth. Don\'t rely on equpment at the resort please. It\'s unpredictable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;8-9 yoga or stretch&lt;br /&gt;&amp;nbsp;9-10 sculpt, yoga or cardio&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;mcePasteBin&quot; style=&quot;position: absolute; top: 29px; left: 0; background: red; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am a runner so I went out the front door the first morning to find that I was in a very affluent area. As I searched for the hotel after going longer than I meant to run, I came across a huge boat dock. It actually turned out to be the dolphin expedition and there were 20 to 30 dolphins and manatees at play. As it turned out, it was within 5 minutes of the hotel lobby! I loved the Oceana restaurant which is adult only.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an update to the above, I\'ve now stayed at Dreams Puerto Aventuras 3 times! I just love the quaint resort with high energy. And it is still a GREAT running area with my favorite little dress shop!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drepa/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/DreamsPuertoAventuras', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
