                [214, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/45595_DRETU.jpg', '', '', 'Tulum', 0, '', 592, 'Linche', 'Orlando', '(52) 984.871.3333', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;$129pppn based on dbl occupancy&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included.&amp;nbsp;Book your round trip ground transportation right here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Cancun-(CUN)-Airport-Transfers-Zone-4/&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 4 Transfers&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
