&lt;p&gt;Monday-Saturday&lt;br /&gt; 9am or 10am (your choice)&amp;nbsp;yoga or pilates &amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; additional morning class of your choice&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Wellness weeks (May and June 2020) two classes per day TBD&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meet with your resort contact to discuss times and locations of classes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Dreams Tulum is an oasis in the jungle.&amp;nbsp; Wow when you walk into the lobby and onto the deck where the bar is situated overlooking the complex you will be blown away. The gym is state of the art and remember that there are adult only restaurants, pools and the disco is adult only at night. Just in case you are not traveling with children or want to get a sitter and enjoy a child-free afternoon or evening. Really great for adult guests.&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/en_us/resorts/mexico/tulum.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsTulum', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you to either&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 436, 491],
                [215, '', '', '', '', '', 'Cancun', 0, '', 592, '', 'Adrian', '', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Cancun, Mexico - CUN&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office. &amp;nbsp;After securing flights, book your round trip transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Cancun-Zone-1/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 1&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;questions regarding trransfers feel free to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot; href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com?subject=Los%20Cabos%20Corridor%20transfers&quot;&gt;email Erica.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Resort hosts 1 yoga/pilates instructor or Zumba teacher each week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Yoga/Pilates or Zumba&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 10:00am yoga/pilates or Zumba&lt;br /&gt; 4:00pm yoga/pilates or Zumba&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; If you are traveling to this resort, provide a flier with your picture, bio and class descriptions. Use our .PDF template - &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.fitbodiesinc.com/pdfs/FitBodies_Instructor.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;HERE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;object width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;344&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/JHETEci-Wdc&amp;amp;hl=en_US&amp;amp;fs=1&amp;amp;&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowFullScreen&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowscriptaccess&quot; value=&quot;always&quot; /&gt;&lt;embed src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/v/JHETEci-Wdc&amp;amp;hl=en_US&amp;amp;fs=1&amp;amp;&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;425&quot; height=&quot;344&quot; /&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;When I walked into the lobby I was impressed.&amp;nbsp; When I walked outside I was dazzled.&amp;nbsp; Seriously, the view goes on forever. You can see the whole strip but you are completely secluded on the point.&amp;nbsp; The dolphins swim in the lagoon right next to the hotel so if you are lucky enough to get a room over looking the lagoon&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drecu/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Cancun%20Resorts/DRECUdolphins.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;DRECU dolphin lagoon&quot; /&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;float: right;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Fit%20Bodies%20photo%20contest/billleedrecuoceanaqua_zps2f790671.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Aqua class at Dreams Cancun&quot; width=&quot;544&quot; height=&quot;193&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drecu/', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/DreamsCancun', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented to your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resort in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico&amp;nbsp;is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 433, 491],
                [216, '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included.&amp;nbsp; A Fit Bodies, Inc. representative will contact you regading transfers.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', 'La Romana', 0, '', 596, 'Martinez', 'Arismendys', '(52) 958.583.0400', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;GX or yoga-stretching is a must. Yoga every 9am. Mon-cardio 12, pilates 4 Tues-aqua 12, cardio 4 Wed.-cardio 12 Thursday aqua 12, cardio 4 Fri cardio 12 Sat. aqua 12, pilates 4&lt;/p&gt;
