&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9:30am-10am and 10am-10:30am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4:30pm-5pm and 5pm-5:30pm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Each hour will consist of two different styles, i.e. 9:30am stretch and 10am cardio, etc.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;***Please do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The near 800 rooms are situated on a beautiful cove.&amp;nbsp; We heard lots of different languages and dialects and apparently this is a very easy destination for European travelers. Tons for the kids and teens to do and lots of area for adults to get away from the kids, too. Amazing beach and ocean (as the below pic shows) is amazing and the resort is very upscale of course.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Fit%20Bodies%20photo%20contest/nicolemauerdrelraquaocean_zpsf1de854b.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Dreams Laromana aqua class&quot; width=&quot;608&quot; height=&quot;238&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drelr/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsLaRomana', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund. We will direct you to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
