                [218, '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included.&amp;nbsp; A Fit Bodies, Inc. representative will contact you regarding transfers.&lt;/p&gt;', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/55398_drpbplogo.jpg', '', 'Cabeza de Toro; P.O. Box 68', 'Higuey', 80, '', 596, 'Manager', 'Entertainment', '809.552.6000', 'info@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Tentative-Yoga every 9am Mon. cardio 12noon,pilates 4 Tues. aqua 12-12:30,cardio 4 Wed. cardio 12 Thurs aqua 12, cardio 4 Fri cardio 12 Sat. aqua 12, pilates 4&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel, after your secure your flight.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Punta-Cana-%28PUJ%29-Airport-Transfers/&quot;&gt;Punta Cana Bavaro Transfers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
