&lt;p&gt;***Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I love the COFFEE in the DR!. There is a coffee shop near the lobby.. The lobby bar is a great hang out also being inside and outside and right near the restaurants. A wonderful socializing area. The pools are great. But my favorite here is the first item of my day and it\'s running on the horse trails. Enjoy!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drepb/index.html', 'Erica', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/DreamsPalmBeach', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
