                [220, '', '', '', '', '', 'Puerto Vallarta', 0, '', 592, 'Gigante', 'Juan', '(52) 322.226.5000', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers from the airport are not included. After securing flights,&amp;nbsp;book your round trip ground transfers online here at&lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/instructor/jumpto/_SL_Travel-Essentials_SL_Puerto-Vallarta-%28PVR%29-Airport-Transfers-Hotel-Zone_SL_/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; FitnessProTravel&lt;/a&gt;. Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Puerto-Vallarta-%28PVR%29-Airport-Transfers-Hotel-Zone/&quot;&gt;Puerto Vallarta South Transfers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt; will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;Resort hosts one pro per week either a yoga teacher, a group fitness,Zumba, pilates teacher or a tennis coach.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;The resort is acquainted with hosting all styles of fitness, mind/body and tennis instructors. Schedule&amp;nbsp;fluctuates&amp;nbsp;based on your specialties. Here\'s what we currently anticipate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mon-Sat&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;y&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;oga &amp;nbsp;and pilates teachers:&lt;/strong&gt; 8am yoga or pilates&lt;br /&gt;9am yoga or pilates&lt;br /&gt; 2 days a week replace one morning class with 4pm sunset yoga or pilates&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;tennis:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;2 hours daily starting at 9:00am&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;group fitness and/or zumba: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;morning cardio&lt;strong&gt; plus late morning aqua&lt;/strong&gt; (times vary depending on the other activities)&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I just got back from Puerto Vallarta and fell in love with the REAL Mexico feel of the city. Dreams is secluded in its own cove in the jungle but it is right down the street from the vibrant village of Puerto Vallarta. You will love this place!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/drepvpromoemailsuzelle_zps071af07a.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Suzelle loves Dreams Puerto Vallarta!&quot; width=&quot;583&quot; height=&quot;382&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/drepvforFPT_zps68f11759.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Share your talents at Dreams Puerto Vallarta&quot; width=&quot;685&quot; height=&quot;260&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drepv/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsPuertoVallarta', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented to your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 439, 494],
                [221, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/57941_DREVM.jpg', '', 'Paseo de los Cocoteros, Lotes 32 y 33', 'Nuevo Vallarta, Nayarit', 0, '', 592, 'Melendez', 'Ramon (Jose)', '(52) 322.226.8700', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers from the airport are not included but you can book them online here. After securing flights, book your transfers online here at FitnessProTravel. Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Puerto-Vallarta-%28PVR%29-Airport-Transfers-Villa-Magna/&quot;&gt;Puerto Vallarta Nuevo Vallarta &lt;/a&gt;Transfers and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica will be in touch via email with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Booking one group exercise instructor, personal trainer, Zumba, yoga or tennis instructor each week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Group Fitness, Zumba and Yoga&lt;br /&gt; 8:00 a.m. &amp;nbsp;Yoga,Zumba or stretch.&lt;br /&gt; 12:00 p.m. &amp;nbsp;Group Aqua. Aqua is not a required format.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tennis Pros&lt;br /&gt; 9:00 and 10:00am clinics and kids camp&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This area of Mexico is very different from Cancun.&amp;nbsp; More traditional and loaded with folklore. The village of Puerto Vallarta is very near.&amp;nbsp; A short flight for the west coast and parts of Texas. I love the view, and sushi, at Gohan&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drenv/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsVillamagna', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you to either&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 439, 494],
                [222, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/63114_DREHU.jpg', '', '', 'Huatulco', 0, '', 592, 'Muller', 'Juan (Pepe)', '(52) 958.583.0400', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&amp;nbsp;After securing flights, book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Huatulco-%28HUX%29-Airport-Transfers/&quot;&gt;Huatulco Transfers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica will be in touch via email with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This resort will host one guest instructor weekly.&amp;nbsp;Teach &lt;em&gt;either&lt;/em&gt; yoga, pilates, general group fitness, personal training, Zumba OR indoor cycle.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Instructors will teach two classes per day, Mon-Sat. The morning class will take place between 7-9am. The evening class will take place between 5-7pm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;***Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The beach is glorious and the resort is a favorite amongst&amp;nbsp;EVERYONE. It\'s truly a wonderful, totally gorgeous enviroment to be in this area of the world!! I highly suggest visiting here!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drehu/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsHuatulco/', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund. &lt;em&gt;We will direct you to either&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
