&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Group Fitness Pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 9:00 &amp;ndash; 10:00 &amp;nbsp;Cardio, Zumba/Dance, Yoga, Pilates&lt;br /&gt; 12:00 Noon Aquasize - half hour&lt;br /&gt; 5:00 - 6:00 &amp;nbsp;Cardio, Zumba/Dance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zumba instructors are required to teach AquaZumba to book this resort.&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tennis pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7:00AM to 10:00AM or 8:00AM to 11:00AM&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I ran into the beachfront of this resort while visiting &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;El Dorado&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; Seaside&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; suites and immediately wanted to talk to the manager about working there.&amp;nbsp; The place is very large built into a jungle-like setting.&amp;nbsp; There is a waterway running through it with footbridge crossings, great nature walkways and even a crocodile area (caged of course).&amp;nbsp; The sports area is very impressive with soccer fields, as well as 4 tennis courts, 2 paddle tennis courts and basketball courts.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.fiestahotelgroup.com/index.php/en/hoteles/destinos/america/mexico/riviera_maya/grand_palladium_kantenah_resort_spa/habitaciones', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented to your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 434, 491],
