', 'http://halfmoon.com/', 'Suzelle', 'info@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments<br><br>This resort requires $150 per week to be paid into the gift fund which will be charged at the time you place your order.', 112, 0, 0],
                [225, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/69980_DRERC.jpg', '', '', 'Puerto Morelas', 0, '', 592, 'Rivas', 'Alex', '(52) 984.875.3000', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Cancun, Mexico.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included with this booking but you can secure online here with us. Have your flight itinerary handy and go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Transfer-Service/&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 1 Transfers &lt;/a&gt;and follow the instructions. Shared and private round trip options available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica will be in touch via email with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Schedule is solidified with Entertainment Management upon arrival to the resort. First format&amp;nbsp;at 8AM. (if you dont teach yoga or pilates you will be asked to lead a stretch class) Second format at 9AM cycle, cardio, sculpt, Zumba, yoga or pilates....(your choice based on the specialties listed on your profile). &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This place will blow you away. I spent time walking the construction site and they have left no stone unturned. In other words, they have thought of everything and more. The beach, the rooms the spa, the fitness center are truly amazing and the pools feel like you are walking right into the sea from the water&amp;rsquo;s edge. Do not miss out on this gem.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drerc/index.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.dreamsresorts.com/drerc/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsRivieraCancun', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 434, 491],
                [226, '&lt;p&gt;Two resorts in one Secrets Wild Orchid and Secrets St. James&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included. Fit Bodies, Inc. will contact you to schedule airport transfers prior to your scheduled trip. In Jamaica we use Jamaica Tours Ltd. (JTL) The desk is located at the back left corner of the Montego Bay Airport. You must schedule your transfers through our office first and then your reservation will be made and your name will be included on their list.&lt;/p&gt;', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/13107_SESMBSJ.jpg', '', 'A59 Montego Freeport', 'Montego Bay', 80, '', 517, 'Bahadure', 'Delrose', '+1 876.953.6600', 'missy@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included with this teaching vacation. You may book your transfer with our partners at JTL-Jamaica Tours Limited online via their website. Click &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to schedule in advance.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Always travel on Sundays to begin teaching on Monday. This resort offers Saturdays off for both the yoga and group fitness instructor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Group Fitness position is&amp;nbsp;one or two classes daily (based on instructor\'s teaching skills). Aqua is required after 2020.&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yoga schedule is two classes daily:&lt;br /&gt;8:30am yoga&lt;br /&gt;5:00 pm yoga or pilates&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Musicians - play poolside from 3:30-5 each day and one evening from 6-7 on stage&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Guests go freely between the two resorts that are connected but have two different lobbies and room design. &lt;em&gt;Amenities are endless and only 20 minutes from the airport.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.secretsresorts.com/', 'Missy Pope', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/SecretsStJames', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires $150 USD per week to be paid into the gift fund and will automatically be charged with your order.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 428, 489],
                [227, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', null, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0],
