&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;One class in the morning at 10:30AM&amp;nbsp; for all specialties. The class is held outdoors on the activity deck daily Monday through Saturday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;The word &amp;ldquo;friendly&amp;rdquo; would describe the feeling of this property while I walked around with the &lt;em&gt;entertainment manager.&amp;nbsp; The guests were enjoying games, socializing at the many bars or lounging by the pool and beach. The quiet pool is just that, but plan on action all day at the dynamic pool. &amp;nbsp;The food is first class, ask for David at Il Piacere, my favorite restaurant. Don\'t miss the cocktail party every night at the patio bar. The seared tuna is amazing. A great place to meet people.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.temptationcancun.com/', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1170112625#!/group.php?gid=56009472588&amp;ref=ts', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires the pro to bring items valued at $225 USD.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Fit Bodies Inc. will contact you with the exact items requested from the resort. &amp;nbsp;Upon traveling, you are required to meet your resort contact Monday morning at 10am and gifts are only to be given to your contact person at the resort.&amp;nbsp;You also may be asked to donate the amount for a more expensive item that requires more than the weekly amount so&amp;nbsp;you would not be required to bring&amp;nbsp;anything.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carryon, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 433, 491],
