                [230, '&lt;p&gt;http://www.breezes.com/resorts/breezes-buzios/ The newest Breezes Resort and the second Breezes Resort to grace the magnificent nation of Brazil. Located in the legendary beach resort town of Buzios in the famous state of Rio de Janeiro, Breezes Resort &amp;amp; Spa &amp;ndash; Buzios offers a spectacular beach, elegant accommodations, one of Latin America&amp;rsquo;s largest swimming pools and so much more. Breezes Resort &amp;amp; Spa &amp;ndash; Buzios is ideal for singles, couples, families of all ages and groups of friends. This is a family resorts, bring one adult guest and up to two children under 12 included in the administration fee. Maximum 3 hours per day Monday through Friday.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', 'was brazil', 0, '', 517, 'Doe', 'John', '', '', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;tbd&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;tbd&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;tbd&lt;/p&gt;', 'breezes-buzios', '', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;tbd&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 431, 490],
