                [233, 'Be ready for a quiet retreat in a luxurious setting.', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', 'You need to provide your own transfer to and from Zoetry Agua.  This  resort is located in  Uvero Alto, on the Eastern coast of the Dominican Republic, just 49 miles, 1  hour and 15 minutes from the airport.  <br>
A taxi ride will cost about $80, each way, before gratuity. ', '', null, 'Teachers at this resort will offer group classes, small group classes and personal sessions with a schedule, which may vary from day to day, based on the needs of resort guests.   No more than three hours per day, allowing plenty of personal relaxation time.  The settings for your classes are like none other in the world!<br />

     ', '<img src="../images/zoetry-logo.jpg" alt="logo" width="175" height="135" align="left" /><p>      <strong>More about the  property:</strong> <br />
