', 'http://www.zoetryresorts.com', 'Lisa', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/ZoetryAguaPuntaCana', 'The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments<br><br>This resort requires $150 of requested item, per week.  Fit Bodies Inc. staff will be in touch with you about a month before your trip to discuss the resort\'s needs. </p>', 111, 0, 0],
                [234, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/78520_NOJRClogo.jpg', '', 'Unidad 26 Mz. 20 Lote 1-1 Sm.3', 'Puerto Morelos Benito Juárez, Quint', 80, '', 592, 'Juarez', 'Alex', '(52) 998 872 8871', 'erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;375 - family - groupx ?and? yoga/pilates&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Cancun, Mexico.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered on this site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After confirming your flights, book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Transfer-Service/&quot;&gt;Cancun Zone 1 Transfers &lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt; will be in touch via with an Amstar Voucher just prior to your depart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For transfer questions, &lt;a title=&quot;Email Erica&quot; href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Contact Erica.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Schedule is finalized with the Entertainment Manager once your are on-site. Classes M-Sat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Group Fitness/ Zumba and Strong Nation classes - 1 or 2 morning classes per day&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tennis Pros: 2 hours&amp;nbsp;each morning&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Golf Pros: 2 hours daily in the morning.&amp;nbsp;There is a three Matt driving range on the top of the roof.&amp;nbsp;Create drills&amp;nbsp;for guests be able to work on short game and long game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I love how large the rooms here are&amp;nbsp;very spacious. There are so many activities, not much time is actually spent in the room though. Walk or run down the beach for miles in one direction, with a marina nearby the other way. Check out the fire show for nightly entertainment!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.nowresorts.com/jade/', 'Erica', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/NowJade', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 434, 491],
                [235, '', '', '', '', 'Carretera Transpeninsular Km 19.5', 'Los Cabos, Baja California Sur,', 80, '23400', 592, 'Angulo', 'Ankara', '(52) 624.145.7700', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Los Cabos, SJD&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Los Cabos, Mexico (SJD)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Transfers - Are not included at this resort.&amp;nbsp; Guest instructors are responsible for transfers to and from the airport. Taxi service will be less than $20 USD each way.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Yoga and or pilates classes tentative 8:30 and 9:30 each day&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resort would like to incorporate meditation session in lieu of a yoga or pilates session, if possible. Pilates instructors who do not teach yoga are welcome at this resort if there is extensive experience in teaching Pilates and some group fitness experience, in order to offer a well rounded program personal to the needs of resort guests. Guest needs at this one of a kind hotel will vary from week to week, therefore the schedule\'s class times may vary.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Zo&amp;euml;try Casa del Mar is a Cond&amp;eacute; Nast Johansens recommended property for 2010.Voted &quot;Mexico&amp;rsquo;s leading golf resort&quot; at the World Travel Awards, Zo&amp;euml;try Casa del Mar has also been recognized among the &quot;World s Best Golf Resorts&quot; by the readers of Conde Nast Traveler and a &quot;Favorite&quot; by the readers of Departures. The Zo&amp;euml;try Casa del Mar staff provides a smiling welcome and pampering care that is our hallmark of hospitality.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.zoetryresorts.com/casadelmar/', 'Lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/reqs.php#!/ZoetryCasaDelMar?ref=mf', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires $150 per week to be paid into the gift fund. A manager will document gift items when you arrive. The resort does not accept cash money in lieu of gifts. Fit Bodies will contact you with their gift requests about a month before you leave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 442, 499],
                [236, '', '', '', '(52) (998) 872 82 99', '', 'Riviera Maya', 0, '', 592, 'Cruz', 'Mario', '(52) (998) 872 82 93', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;Interested in sensuality experts as well $500&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Cancun, Mexico.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&lt;/p&gt;
