&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt; will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For transfer questions, &lt;a title=&quot;Email Erica&quot; href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Contact Erica.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Group Fitness and Yoga Teachers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 10:30am and 3:30am Monday through Friday.&amp;nbsp;You will send your suggested schedule to your resort contact, along with your flyer, at least 2 weeks prior to departing for approval.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;After spending the day at this property, I am so excited to be able to offer this hotel to our pros. Desire is a very upscale couples only and clothing optional location on the beautiful beach of Puerto Morales in the Riviera Maya. Chill out or party hard at this one of a kind resort.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s50.photobucket.com/user/Sugarscreens/media/Desire%20Resort%20and%20Spa/desire_riviera_gallery4_zps5b216989.jpg.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Desire%20Resort%20and%20Spa/desire_riviera_gallery4_zps5b216989.jpg&quot; alt=&quot; photo desire_riviera_gallery4_zps5b216989.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s50.photobucket.com/user/Sugarscreens/media/Desire%20Resort%20and%20Spa/desire_riviera_gallery3_zpsac93541f.jpg.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Desire%20Resort%20and%20Spa/desire_riviera_gallery3_zpsac93541f.jpg&quot; alt=&quot; photo desire_riviera_gallery3_zpsac93541f.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.desirecancun.com/', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/DesireResorts', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $200 per week to be presented to Mario, your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resort in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico&amp;nbsp;is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 434, 491],
                [237, '', '', '', '', 'One Ritz-Carlton Drive', 'Rose Hall, St. James  Jamaica, W.I.', 80, '', 517, 'Vaswani', 'Vishal', '876 953 2800', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are not included with this teaching vacation. You may book your transfer with our partners at JTL-Jamaica Tours Limited online via their website. Click&amp;nbsp;to schedule in advance&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Schedule is dependent on number of pros on property and particular seasons (weather). Exact schedule will fluctuate from one week to the next and Fit Bodies Inc. will be coordinating your schedule in advance.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Group fitness pros&lt;/strong&gt; - lead cardio, sculpt and aqua classes. Expect to teach 1 kids fitness classes each week unless a Kids Fitness Instructor is on property. Two afternoon off during the week.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Yoga/Pilates pros&lt;/strong&gt; - lead yoga or pilates classes to resort guests. Expect to teach 1 kids yoga or teen pilates classes each week unless a Kids Fitness Instructor is on property.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Kids Fitness Pro&lt;/strong&gt; - lead 2 or 3 45 minute classes per day to children ages 4-12.&lt;br /&gt;
All positions will have at one afternoon off and are generally 2 classes per day.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Tennis Pro&lt;/strong&gt; - Two hours each morning except Thursday.&amp;nbsp; Thur is round robin tourney hosted by guest tennis professional.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://s50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Cancun%20Resorts/Jamaica%20Resorts/?action=view¤t=IMG_0367.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Meditation at Ritz Carlton&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Cancun%20Resorts/Jamaica%20Resorts/IMG_0367.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I love this resort. This is where I stay when I am in Montego Bay. I enjoy the trade wind that is always blowing as you teach your classes overlooking the Caribbean. I always set up my office in the Cohoba Lounge with a glass of wine, a bowl of nuts and fabulous people watching.&lt;br /&gt;
