&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Schedule is finalized with the Entertainment Manager once your are on-site.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Yoga and Fitness Instructors: 2 classes per day.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
