&lt;p&gt;TTHSat 8am and 9am&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I visited this resort right after it was named Now Sapphire. I would eye the property as I ran past when it was the Paridisus and loved how it looked from afar. I was equally impressed when I toured the facility. Huge pools, wonderfully placed restaurants and the rooms are brightly decorated to add to the flavor. Hands down an incredible location for families, singles or couples. The Mayan inspired decor and architecture really takes you to a different world!&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.nowresorts.com/sapphire/', 'Erica', '', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
