&lt;p&gt;Tennis Pros - offer clinics and lessons&amp;nbsp;- 9am-11am&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;*Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;div class=&quot;marginT&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Suzelle\'s Comments:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;I LOVE Puerto Vallarta! This resort fits perfectly between the airport and downtown Puerto Vallarta with expansive beach and great pools. &amp;nbsp;Very upscale family resort and adults have dining and activities for them next door at Secrets Vallarta Bay, the adult only resort. &amp;nbsp;Now Amber Puerto Vallarta will host diverse fitness specialties and all rooms have ocean view. &amp;nbsp;How can you beat that?! &amp;nbsp;I was most amazed at the high number of vegetarian items offered at the restaurants. &amp;nbsp;Lot of dining variety and the service is exquisite everywhere! &amp;nbsp;On my last day, I overheard my favorite quote of the week. &amp;nbsp;A man turned to his companion and friends and said, &quot;Do you want to watch the sunset from the pool, beach, lobby, room or restaurant?&quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;marginT&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.nowresorts.com/amber/', 'Erica', '', 'http://www.facebook.com/NowAmberPuertoVallarta', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you to either&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
