                [255, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/45697_SEVPV.jpg', '', '', 'Puerto Vallarta', 0, '', 592, 'Gigante', 'Juan', '', 'missy@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transportation - Fly into Puerto Vallarta, Mexico. PVR airport code.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included with bookings at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office. This is booked &lt;a href=&quot;https://fitnessprotravel.com/shop/Travel-Essentials/Puerto-Vallarta-(PVR)-Airport-Transfers/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;PVR hotel zone transfers&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; on this site and we\'ll send you an email with those instructions to secure ground transportation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Teach Monday-Saturday, 1 or two classes&amp;nbsp;daily. Mostly morning only. Schedule is finalized once onsite, with the Entertainment manager. If you are a personal trainer, the schedule is working in \'small\' groups with guests.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;Yoga Teachers expect one 9am class M-Sat&lt;br /&gt;Cycle Instructors - Spin bikes will be placed in an outside area&lt;br /&gt;Tennis pros - one or two hours of clinics or lessons each day.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This resort is perfectly situated about a mile outside of the city and on a beautiful beach. The sunset views are spectacular. Love to take a run each morning through the oceanfront art collection. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.secretsresorts.com/vallarta-bay-puerto-vallarta', 'Missy Pope', '', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
