&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 433, 491],
                [257, '', '', '', '', '', 'Cancun', 80, '', 592, '', 'Unknown', '', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Are not included&amp;nbsp;in Mexico.&amp;nbsp;However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&amp;nbsp;Book your round trip transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel. &amp;nbsp;Once your location has been confirmed you will receive an email in regards to the Zone to book from the&amp;nbsp;Pro Shop tab.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;1 to 2 classes per day schedule TBD&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;LOVE THEM ALL!!!&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Lisa Snowden', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All professionals will pay into the gift fund - $150.00&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The resort will normally request items for you to take.&amp;nbsp; As soon as&amp;nbsp;we&amp;nbsp;receive the request&amp;nbsp;we will notify you and will&amp;nbsp;ship items to&amp;nbsp;you. &amp;nbsp;Plan on taking the items with you in your checked bags or carry on. &amp;nbsp;But, do&amp;nbsp;not assume the items will always fit in a carry on.&amp;nbsp; Shipping to the resort is not permitted. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 433, 491],
                [258, '', '', '', '', 'Unknown', 'Punta Cana', 0, '', 596, '', 'Unknown', '', 'suzelle@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Airport Transfers&amp;nbsp;not included&amp;nbsp;in Punta Cana.&amp;nbsp;However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&amp;nbsp;Book your round trip transfers right online here at &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Pro-Shop/&quot;&gt;FitnessProTravel.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;Once your location has been confirmed you will receive an email in regards to the Zone to book from the&amp;nbsp;Pro Shop tab.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;TBD&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', 'Suzelle', 'suzelle@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All professionals will pay into the gift fund - $150.00&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The resort will normally request items&amp;nbsp;for you to take.&amp;nbsp; As soon as&amp;nbsp;we&amp;nbsp;receive the request&amp;nbsp;we will notify you and will&amp;nbsp;ship items to&amp;nbsp;you. &amp;nbsp;Plan on&amp;nbsp;taking the items with you in your checked bags or carry on. &amp;nbsp;But, do&amp;nbsp;not assume the items will always fit in a carry on.&amp;nbsp; Shipping to the resort is not permitted. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 435, 495],
                [259, '', '', '', '', '', 'Tortola', 84, '', 516, 'Reid', 'Safyie', '', 'suzelle@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;div class=&quot;marginT&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: verdana, arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Terrance B. Lettsome International Airport (EIS) Transfers&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guests may fly into Beef Island Airport, Tortola (EIS) via San Juan (SJU), St. Thomas (STT), Antigua (ANU), or St. Maarten (SXM), from Beef Island Airport, guests transfer to Peter Island via the resort private yacht. Transfers from Beef Island Airport are $60 per person for stays in 2011. This transfer can be reserved any day, and at any time. You will contact the Reservations department with arrival information in advance.&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: verdana, arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;&quot; /&gt; Peter Island Resort private ferry will be available on Tuesdays and Saturdays to meet guests who fly directly to St. Thomas, U.S.V.I. The total elapsed time of this beautiful trip by luxury ferry is typically 1 1/2 hours including all customs clearance. The ferry leaves from Charlotte Amalie (a short ten-minute cab ride from the airport) which is coordinated through the Tropic Tours Taxi desk at Ground Transportation at Cyril E. King International Airport and arrives at the Peter Island Resort &amp;amp; Spa Marina. The ride is through some of the most beautiful sailing waters in the Caribbean. The times have been arranged to allow for an easy 2 1/2 hour arrival to the airport on departure day and a leisurely 2 hours from the arrival at the St. Thomas airport.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;group fitness instructors (requested yoga or pilates experience)&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: verdana, arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;&quot; /&gt; 9:30am yoga or pilates&lt;br /&gt; 10:45-11:30am aqua or core/sculpt&lt;br /&gt; 4:30pm - pro\'s choice&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;div class=&quot;paddingLR&quot; style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: verdana, arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 20px 0px 20px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;marginT&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;This is by far one of the most exotic and luxurious resorts we have made available to our pros. We are looking for the best of the best so if you fit that bill please book this resort.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;', 'http://peterisland.com', 'Suzelle', 'suzelle@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;$150 gift fund per week is automatically added to your order.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created at this program\'s inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 449, 500],
                [260, '', '', '', '', '4 Cooma Cain Road, Mountain Pine Ridge', 'Cayo District,', 80, '', 517, 'Johnson', 'Amon', '1-866-443-3364', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;From Belize City (BZE) Road transfers will be arranged by our office via your Fit Bodies, Inc. concierge once you have secured airfare.&amp;nbsp; Transfers are $30 per person each way and will be paid for at the resort.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Two yoga classes per day consisting of sunrise yoga and afternoon yoga on any of the three platforms as well as on excursion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Class schedule will change based on the needs of the resort guests as often appointments are made by guests and cleared with the teacher. Therefore, flexibility in teachers schedule is a must! &amp;nbsp;FUN! &amp;nbsp;FUN! &amp;nbsp;Yogis LOVE Hidden Valley Inn!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Personal Trainers&lt;/em&gt;: Will work one on one with guests or work in small groups totally based on the needs of this petite resort\'s discerning guests. Two hours of teaching time daily.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Massage Therapists&lt;/em&gt;: Will work with the certified and experienced spa staff to enhance and expend upon the services already offered. &amp;nbsp;The position will offer a couple longer days spent with the massage staff then complete days off to enjoy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is our first non-beach property. The waterfalls, hiking trails and mountain vistas are spectacular and welcoming to the adventurous soul.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Belize/?action=view&amp;amp;current=HiddenValleymap.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;height: 266px; width: 347px;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Belize/HiddenValleymap.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Photobucket&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Belize/?action=view&amp;amp;current=birdinghummerhidden.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;height: 264px; width: 352px;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Belize/birdinghummerhidden.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Photobucket&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.hiddenvalleyinn.com/', 'Lisa', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/HiddenValleyInn', '&lt;p&gt;Equipment fund of $150 is included with the checkout process to book this teaching vacation.&amp;nbsp;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 447, 501],
                [261, '', '', '', '', '', 'Puerto Vallarta', 0, '', 592, '', 'Fabian', '011 52 3292 269900', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers &lt;/strong&gt;- Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office. Only private transfer service if offfered through our partner, Amstar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After you book flights, secure transfer here on&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Puerto-Vallarta-(PVR)-Airport-Transfers-North-Zone/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;FitnessProTravel.&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once you book this resort, Go to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Pro-Shop/&quot;&gt;Pro Shop Tab&lt;/a&gt; on your account page and choose&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: blue;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Puerto-Vallarta-%28PVR%29-Airport-Transfers-North-Zone/&quot;&gt;Puerto Vallarta (PVR) Airport Transfers North Zone&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
