&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!--EndFragment--&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select Quantiy of 1, for up to 8 passengers. Provide flight info during checkout. Erica will email you a confirmation voucher prior to trip departure. Contact Erica at &lt;a href=&quot;erica@fitbodiesinc.com&quot;&gt;Erica@fitbodiesinc.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fitness Pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 10:00 - 10:30 Yoga, Pilates or Stretch&lt;br /&gt; 11:00 - 11:30 Cardio of your choice&lt;br /&gt; 12:00 - 12:30 Noon Aquasize&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Tennis pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 3 hours each morning. You will get to decide (within reason) what time you will start. For example 8AM for 3 hours or 9AM for 3 hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Time for off site excursion can be arranged with the Entertainment Manager once on property.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;The windy road to Punta Mita is gorgeous, with wonderful views of the Pacific ocean and luxury real estate along the way. The beach goes on forever and the pristine community feel of the area makes it comfortable to travel alone or with your friends or family. Grand Palladium Vallarta is definitely a 5 star resort doing a wonderful job catering to families, singles and friends alike. Lisa and I visited Puerto Vallarta and she &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lisaowens.com/2012/04/fit-bodies-inc-day-one-in-puerto-vallarta-grand-palladium-vallarta/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;wrote all about this resort in her blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;float: left; height: 299px; width: 250px;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Puerto Vallarta April 2012/GPVallartamoresurfshop.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Surf shop at Grand Palladiun Vallarta&quot; /&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;float: right; height: 221px; width: 400px;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Puerto Vallarta April 2012/GPVallartalargebeach.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Private surf beach at Grand Palladium Vallarta&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.fiestahotelgroup.com/en/hotels/destination/america/mexico/riviera-nayarit/palladium-vallarta-resort-spa/', 'Denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This resort requires pros to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented to your resort contact. Fit Bodies, Inc. will be in touch within a month of your travel with specific items.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 439, 494],
                [262, '', '', '', '', '1 Rhine Road', 'Maho Bay', 0, '', 0, 'Fanis', 'Jardin', '721-545-2115', 'serenityspa@mahobeach.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Sonesta Maho Beach Resort is a 5 minute ride from the Princess Juliana airport. Upon arrival you will follow the signs to ground transportation, and hire a taxi. Estmated price $7.00 USD&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Two &amp;nbsp;classes a day (Times are tentative and subject to change)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will teach a morning yoga and afternoon cardio format (Zumba, kick boxing, Tabata, Boot Camp, your choice)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are so excited to have a resort in St. Maarten. &amp;nbsp; The location is wonderful, the beach and pool areas are great. &amp;nbsp; We found a great spot to watch the sunset &amp;nbsp;and the planes arriving and departing right out on the veranda.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.sonesta.com/MahoBeach/', 'Denise Cox', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This resort requires the pro to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented on Monday to the entertainment manager. Fit Bodies, Inc will be in touch with specific items within one month of your departure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to St. Martin is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 450, 507],
                [263, '', '', '', '', '', 'Ocho Rios', 0, '', 517, 'Lawrence', 'Marike', '', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers are included.&amp;nbsp;Stop by the Sandals&amp;nbsp;desk at the Montego Bay airport to where an airconditioned shuttle will take you to your destination and return to the airport at the end of your stay.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Yoga teachers:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Monday, Wednesday, Friday 5-6 pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tuesday, Thursday 7-8am&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This is one of the most elegant resorts you will ever enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Denise', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires $150 per week to be paid into the gift fund.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 427, 489],
                [264, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/58724_DRELC.jpg', '', 'Carretera Transpeninsular CSL-SJC Km 18.5 Los Cabos', 'Baja California Sur', 0, '', 592, '', 'Jesus', '52 624-145-7600', '', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office. &amp;nbsp;After securing flights, book your round trip transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Los-Cabos-%28SJD%29-Airport-Transfers-Corridor-Zone/&quot;&gt;Los Cabos Corridor Transfers&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Resort hosts 1 group fitness, peronsl trainer, yoga/pilates instructor or Zumba teacher each week. Classes held Monday-Saturday&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yoga / Pilates Instructors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;8am yoga or pilates&lt;br /&gt;9:30am yoga or pilates&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Group Fitness / Zumba Instructors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;8am stretch&lt;br /&gt;9:30am cardio class&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;***Do not rely on the Explorer Club during your&amp;nbsp;class time obligations.&amp;nbsp;Babysitting is available for a fee and must be arranged&amp;nbsp;if your child cannot be supervised&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;your companion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;What a gorgeous property. The beach is huge and the golden hacienda style building is absolutely breathtaking.&amp;nbsp; I love the adult pool and restaurant that was recently added.&amp;nbsp; The serenity there is a wonderful option when you want to get away from the other activities. LOVE CABO!!&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://dreamsresorts.com/drelc/index.html', 'Erica@fitbodiesinc.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/DreamsLosCabos', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 442, 499],
                [265, '', '', '', '', 'Carretera Transpeninsular Km 21.5', 'Fracc Cabo Real  San Jose del Cabo', 80, '23400', 592, 'Valdez', 'Miguel', '(52) 624.14.4.2000', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt; - Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered through the Fit Bodies office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Book your transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel.&amp;nbsp; Go to Pro Shop tab and choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://fitnessprotravel.com/Travel-Essentials/Los-Cabos-%28SJD%29-Airport-Transfers-Corridor-Zone/&quot;&gt;Los Cabos Corridor Transfers&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com%20?subject=Cancun%20Zone%201%20transfers&quot;&gt;Erica&lt;/a&gt; will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; please &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:erica@fitbodiesinc.com?subject=Los%20Cabos%20Private%20Transfer%20service&quot;&gt;email Erica.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Yoga and pilates teachers will typically teach two morning classes, back to back. and possibly a few sunset classes for a total of two daily classes. &amp;nbsp; The schedule is intentionally light to have space for private requests or special needs. Group fitness instructors need to teach a stretch or mind/body format, aqua and some sort of cardio. The reviews from instructors (see reviews toward top of this page) does a nice job of outlining the schedule flucuations.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This resort is spectacular. And very popular amongst instructors and regular guests alike. Not uncommon for the resort to block dates in advance so don\'t hesitate to secure your spot; make sure you don\'t lose a great travel session over the resort selling out in advance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.secretsresorts.com/marquis/', 'Lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'lisa@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/SecretsMarquis', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires the pro to bring items valued at $150 per week to be presented on Monday to the entertainment manager. Your Fit Bodies, Inc concierge will be in touch with specific items within one month of your departure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The gift items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage, so please plan accordingly. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Mexico is extremely&amp;nbsp;expensive and the very&amp;nbsp;reason the&amp;nbsp;gift fund was created.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 442, 499],
                [266, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/95420_SEPLC.jpg', '', 'Puerto Los Cabos, San Jose del Cabo', 'Baja California Sur, Mexico', 80, '', 592, 'Maldonado', 'David', '', 'missy@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;- Are not included at this resort. However, transfer services are offered on this website. After securing flights, book your round trip transfers right online here at FitnessProTravel. Go to Pro Shop tab and choose&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://fitnessprotravel.com/shop/Travel-Essentials/Los-Cabos-(SJD)-Airport-Transfers-Zone-1/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Los Cabos (SJD) Airport Transfers Zone 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow the instructions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Erica&amp;nbsp;will be in touch with an Amstar Voucher before you depart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Hosting a yoga teacher every week. Teach back to back classes in the morning, 45 minutes each. Offering two different formats is wonderful. Then yoga for first class and second format, like sculpting for example, would be great. The entertainment manager finalizes schedule on property.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff;&quot;&gt;*July 14-October 28, 2018 special opportunities: resort welcomes non-yoga teachers who offer group fitness classes, or Zumba instructors. Yoga teachers always welcome to book. Non-yoga teacher schedules are not yet confirmed and may vary based on specific formats you teach. Two classes daily is anticipated on all non-travel days.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;There is nothing like Los Cabos!! Walking on the beach is a must, at least down to the marina. I\'d get my morning run in this way each morning. Amazing weather year round and every sunset has the same gorgeous continuity.&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.secretsresorts.com/puerto-los-cabos', 'Missy Pope', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/SecretsPuertoLosCabosMX?fref=ts', '&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Within the month of your departure date, you will be contacted by our office and instructed how to handle the gift fund.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;We will direct you&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;1. Purchase specific, requested items totalling $150USD based on the needs of the resort.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;These requested items will be brought to the resorts&amp;nbsp;in your checked baggage or carry-on, so please plan accordingly. Shipping to these countries&amp;nbsp;is not an option.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;2. Purchase the Mandatory $150USD package in the Pro Shop. This occurs when items are requested well over the $150 amount so we collect from many guest instructors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they need&amp;nbsp;for operations in the entertainment and fitness departments. Resorts provide us with a list of specific items to delegate to each traveling pro. Including the gift fund for every week and every instructor is a long-standing and mandatory tradition of Fit Bodies, Inc. programming.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 442, 499],
                [267, '', '', '', '(876) 974-5700', 'P.O. Box 771, Main Street,', 'Ocho Rios', 0, '', 517, 'Lattery', 'Nicola', '1(876)974-5691', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;Transportation - Fly into Montego Bay, Jamaica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;Transfers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;- Are&amp;nbsp; included at this resort. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Monday through Friday &amp;nbsp;(no classes on Saturday)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;8am power walk, dynamic stretch or yoga&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;11am -11:30am&amp;nbsp;aqua fitness&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3 or 4pm cardio of choice&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&quot;I love my morning run around the 100 acres of lush mountainside where the villas are located and on through the pier and beach area. The Reef Terrace is my favorite restaurant overlooking the sea serving Caribbean and Jamaica cuisine and i love the Sundowner lounge with a perfect view of the sunset. You will be wowed by the decor and equally impressed with everything about this resort.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 400px; height: 300px; float: left;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Sandals Resorts/pierinthelightphoto.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Sunny Pier&quot; /&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 240px; height: 320px; float: right;&quot; src=&quot;http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f349/Sugarscreens/Sandals Resorts/sandalsgranderivierapoolhouse.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Sandals Grande Riviera Poolhouse&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'http://www.sandals.com/', 'Denise', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Fans-of-Sandals-Grande-Riviera-Sandals-Grande-Ocho-Rios/179766952072250', '&lt;p&gt;A gift fee of $150 will be collected at time of reserving your week. &amp;nbsp;From time to time the resort will request items to be brought. &amp;nbsp;If this should happen, we will ship the items to you to be taken with you to the resort. &amp;nbsp;The items will need to be packed in your checked bags, so do plan on checking a bag if this occurs. &amp;nbsp;Shipping to Jamaica is extremely expensive and is not an option.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 428, 489],
                [268, '', '', '', '', 'Rose Hall Rd', 'Montego Bay', 80, '', 517, 'Welcome', 'Alex', '876 953 2800', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Transfers not included.&amp;nbsp; You may book and pay for your transfers to and from MBJ, &amp;nbsp;Donald Sangster International airport, via the following link:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&quot;&gt;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Monday through Saturday&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expect&amp;nbsp;one morning and one afternoon class. &amp;nbsp;The schedule always finalized upon arrival.&amp;nbsp; Class held in the gym, beach or pier on either the adult or family side.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;span&gt;We were so sad when The Ritz-Carlon Rose Hall closed it\'s doors. Yet, Hyatt has done an AMAZING job. Keeping the original charm, while adding more of it and still the service is impeccable. These folks do it right and we are honored for you to share your teaching skills with these discerning guests. Recently, I booked the Zilara position and my daughter in law booked Ziva so we had a family vacation where it\'s very easy to comingle, especially adults going over to the Ziva side. That\'s where evening entertainment and some&amp;nbsp;of the dining is anyway.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;', 'http://rosehall.ziva.hyatt.com/en/hotel/home.html', 'Denise Cox', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Fit Bodies, Inc. created the gift fund at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; This resort requires pros&amp;nbsp;to pay $150 into a gift fund, and you may receive a request to take items to the resort by our office, using these funds. If requested to bring items, we\'ll communicate with you in advance, and those items will travel to your doorstep and then in your luggage.&lt;/p&gt;', 112, 428, 489],
                [269, '', '', 'https://fitnessprotravel.com/files/13532_HyattZilaraRoseHalllogo.jpg', '', 'Rose Hall Rd', 'Montego Bay', 80, '', 517, 'Welcome', 'Alex', '876 953 2800', 'denise@fitbodiesinc.com', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Airport transfers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;are not included&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;for this resort. You are able to book your transfers to and from MBJ, &amp;nbsp;Donald Sangster International airport, via the following link:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.jamaicatoursltd.com/transfer.php?type=airport_transfer&amp;amp;affiliateid=1&amp;amp;ht=&amp;amp;refresh=1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;Monday through Saturday&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expect&amp;nbsp;one morning and one afternoon class. &amp;nbsp;All is determined upon arrival.&amp;nbsp; Class held in the gym, beach or pier on either the adult or family side.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'We were so sad when The Ritz-Carlon Rose Hall closed it\'s doors. Yet, Hyatt has done an AMAZING job. Keeping the original charm, while adding more of it and still the service is impeccable. These folks do it right and we are honored for you to share your teaching skills with these discerning guests.', 'http://rosehall.zilara.hyatt.com/en/hotel/home.html', 'Denise Cox', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This resort requires pros&amp;nbsp;pay $150 USD into a gift fund, and you may be asked to take items to the resort by our office, using these funds. If you are asked to take items, we\'ll communicate with you in advance and those items will travel to your doorstep and then in your luggage.&lt;/p&gt;', 111, 428, 489],
