&lt;p&gt;Purchasing a trip to a Sandals&amp;nbsp;Resort is confirmed differently than all of our other resorts.&amp;nbsp; Once you purchase your week,&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Sandals will process the request 2 weeks before arrival, a confirmation number will be issued 7-10 days before arrival.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Airline tickets should only be purchased after you receive a confirmation.&amp;nbsp; We do understand your airline flights may increase in price however we want to ensure you will have a confirmed room. &amp;nbsp;Sandals has requested a professional for the dates advertised and it is their intent to have a guest professional.&amp;nbsp; If Sandals is unable to confirm your room, you will have a credit on your account for one year from date of purchase to be used for any available resort for any available date within your membership level.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A refund will not be issued&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&amp;nbsp; Our staff will ensure you are contacted the moment we receive a confirmation.&amp;nbsp; Promise!&amp;nbsp; To ensure you receive a prompt reply to your email requesting an update on the status of your confirmation,&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;an auto-reply has been set in place - &amp;nbsp;Confirmation has not yet been received, thank you for checking!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The stately palms that grace the mile-long entrance into the legendary La Toc Estate and golf resort are the awe-inspiring prelude to your &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sandals.com/destinations/stlucia.cfm&quot;&gt;St. Lucia vacation&lt;/a&gt; at the Caribbean\'s Most Glamorous Resort, Sandals La Toc. Recognized as the most sparkling jewel in the islands, the &quot;Emerald of the Caribbean&quot; glitters invitingly along the half-mile crescent shaped beach, cradling exotic coral bluffs, lush hillsides, and rolling fairways&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Share your teaching talents at this luxury resort where everything is included.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', 'St Lucia has 2 international airports Hweanorra Airport UVF - 2 hour transfer from the resort Vigie Airport&amp;nbsp; SLU 15-20 minutes from the resort Transfers&amp;nbsp;- Are&amp;nbsp; included at this resort. from both airports', '', null, 'Monday through Friday.&amp;nbsp; Saturdays off! &lt;br /&gt;8:00am- Powerwalk, yoga or stretch &lt;br /&gt;11:00am-11:30 - aqua fitness &lt;br /&gt;3:00 gym assistance (some days) &lt;br /&gt;4:00-4:30 cardio of choice', 'Sandals asks us to send special fitness and tennis professionals&amp;nbsp;to cover the classes when their staff takes off for vacation. I hope that special person is you!', 'http://www.sandals.com/main/lucia/lu-home.cfm', '', '', '', 'The gift fund was created by Fit Bodies, Inc. at its inception as a gesture of kindness toward the resorts hosting each pro. These resorts, no matter how large and how prestigious, do not have a budget for certain items they desire and require for the day to day operations in the entertainment and fitness departments &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This resort requires $150 per week to be paid into the gift fund.', 111, 457, 501],
