                [540, '', '', '', '', '1 East 11th St.', 'Riviera Beach', 10, '', 1, '', 'Nasreen', '(800) 374-4363', '', '', '', '&lt;span&gt;Terminal Address: Port of Palm Beach 1 East 11th Street Riviera Beach, FL 33404&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Flying- PBI West Palm Beach International and take a taxi or uber the 10 minutes to the port.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Driving -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;Coming from the north&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span&gt;From I-95 South take Exit 76, Blue Heron Boulevard, and proceed east to US Highway 1 (Broadway). Turn right (heading south) onto U.S. Highway 1. Proceed approximately one mile south and make a left on East 11th Street (located at the north end of the bridge).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;Coming from the south&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span&gt;From I-95 North take Exit 74, 45th Street, and proceed east to US Highway 1 (Broadway). Turn left (heading north) onto US Highway 1. Proceed approximately one mile north over the Skypass Bridge to East 11th Street (located at the north end of the bridge) and turn right.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Parking -&amp;nbsp;The benefits of sailing with us start as soon as you arrive at our exclusive terminal located at the Port of Palm Beach. With convenient at-the door valet parking, you will quickly be on your way. One of&amp;nbsp;the parking attendants will meet you as soon as you arrive at the cruise terminal.&amp;nbsp;Only $19 a night!&lt;/span&gt;', '', null, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set sail from Port of Palm Beach - one afternoon class&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
